uint8_t SDMMC004_LocalLockStructType::PwdData[SDMMC004_MAX_PASSWD_LENGTH *2]

In case of setting a new password, it contains the new password. In case of a password change, it contains the old password followed by the new password.

Definition at line 1595 of file SDMMC004.h.

uint8_t SDMMC004_LocalLockStructType::PwdLen

Defines the following password(s) length (in bytes). In case of a password change, this field includes the total password lengths of old and new passwords.
